333adccb-d91b-44bf-a3de-d0d2fab7d885.title: Arthur the Clue Hunter
333adccb-d91b-44bf-a3de-d0d2fab7d885.text: What can I do for you?

options.text: Ask about the types of clues.

db12e255-56c9-4f03-b13d-aca13f0f8f3d.title: Arthur the Clue Hunter
db12e255-56c9-4f03-b13d-aca13f0f8f3d.text:
Beginner clues are the lowest tier of clue scroll and as
such only require a couple of steps to solve.

2d76961c-c6f0-4846-b4e5-b09cc64a39b3.title: Arthur the Clue Hunter
2d76961c-c6f0-4846-b4e5-b09cc64a39b3.text:
Beginner clues are gained through various activities.
Those activities are as follows.

32b731ff-5340-400d-aff2-78f47508e9f8.title: Arthur the Clue Hunter
32b731ff-5340-400d-aff2-78f47508e9f8.text:
Slaying monsters for a chance at a clue being dropped.
I hear goblins are sneaky, maybe they have some clue
scrolls on them ripe for the taking.

173933e3-288f-4b05-a8f7-75dc5c76dd87.title: Arthur the Clue Hunter
173933e3-288f-4b05-a8f7-75dc5c76dd87.text:
Maybe someone left one in the cow field, who knows
where you could obtain them.

9b10a75f-58e6-40ae-bc5f-eaa0bfde20ab.title: Arthur the Clue Hunter
9b10a75f-58e6-40ae-bc5f-eaa0bfde20ab.text:
Beginner clues have also been known to be left in]
geodes while mining, as well as sometimes in bottles that
you may fish up from time to time and from nests
which fall out of trees.

e3905f7c-b7ba-44cf-845b-046e73816eb7.title: Arthur the Clue Hunter
e3905f7c-b7ba-44cf-845b-046e73816eb7.text: Although this is a much rarer occurrence.

7186e48a-5354-414f-a58b-2d5cda535037.title: Arthur the Clue Hunter
7186e48a-5354-414f-a58b-2d5cda535037.text:
Unlike more advanced clues, you should not expect to
get very valuable items from completing a beginner
clue.

6211832f-b8f0-4926-9c18-be1315f12533.title: Arthur the Clue Hunter
6211832f-b8f0-4926-9c18-be1315f12533.text: Advanced clues have tiers between easy and master.

597b82d8-1596-4651-bba9-124b49d55764.title: Arthur the Clue Hunter
597b82d8-1596-4651-bba9-124b49d55764.text:
You can gain advanced clues by the same way you would get
 a beginner clue. But to get higher tier scrolls you
will need to defeat more powerful foes.

c44ed43a-e103-4caa-aee7-3e93144a4c3a.title: Arthur the Clue Hunter
c44ed43a-e103-4caa-aee7-3e93144a4c3a.text:
The chance to get a higher tier clue from geodes,
bottles and nests is lower the higher  the tier. But if you
chop down higher-level trees you will have a higher
chance of receiving a nest which contains a clue. Same

94945f76-5b70-48a0-b8f0-dc7e1f87359d.title: Arthur the Clue Hunter
94945f76-5b70-48a0-b8f0-dc7e1f87359d.text: The only exception to this is master clue scrolls.

b227ba59-1940-4bdd-b030-879c75106070.title: Arthur the Clue Hunter
b227ba59-1940-4bdd-b030-879c75106070.text:
Master clues can only be obtained as a rare chance when opening
your casket or by handing in one of every type of clue, apart from
beginner, to Watson who resides in Hosidius.

2c4ba6de-13da-4f56-b5e3-8812d694674e.title: Arthur the Clue Hunter
2c4ba6de-13da-4f56-b5e3-8812d694674e.text: But with more advanced tiers of clue, come better loot.

ed31bcd5-8635-4c9c-98c6-9d567a3c15a5.title: Arthur the Clue Hunter
ed31bcd5-8635-4c9c-98c6-9d567a3c15a5.text: So long and happy clue hunting!

4f9b2cbc-c602-4f20-8fca-906a5b378d65.title: <player>
4f9b2cbc-c602-4f20-8fca-906a5b378d65.text:
Hey Arthur, can I start receiving clue from vessels?
They're clogging up my backpack!

5844500f-2e5d-4ea0-abba-ba40c97ebc59.title: Arthur the Clue Hunter
5844500f-2e5d-4ea0-abba-ba40c97ebc59.text:
Vessel containers include mining geodes, fishing bottles
and clue nests. Are you sure you want to start
receiving them, again?

03bb69c6-07a5-421d-aa2c-086aea435d5c.title: <player>
03bb69c6-07a5-421d-aa2c-086aea435d5c.text:
Hey Arthur, can I stop receiving clue from vessels?
They're clogging up my backpack!

9239939e-7fbf-4baf-9c96-489b9eaadbd9.title: Arthur the Clue Hunter
9239939e-7fbf-4baf-9c96-489b9eaadbd9.text:
Vessel containers include mining geodes, fishing bottles
and clue nests. Are you sure you want to stop
receiving them?

options.text: Yes please, I want to stop receiving vesseled containers.
Yes please, I want to start receiving vesseled containers.

9571df66-0ecb-418b-bd99-6118fc16a517.title: <player>
9571df66-0ecb-418b-bd99-6118fc16a517.text: Yes please, I want to start receiving vesseled containers.

fa45f396-31a7-4ce4-8077-8eb400b38b83.title: Arthur the Clue Hunter
fa45f396-31a7-4ce4-8077-8eb400b38b83.text:
Very well, you'll now find clues from mining, fishing
and woodcutting.

1d0b09fd-c8ea-4d1e-b923-8b90b71e9774.title: Arthur the Clue Hunter
1d0b09fd-c8ea-4d1e-b923-8b90b71e9774.text: Is there anything else I can help you with?

a4d10e12-ee9d-4967-9baa-54f37a016607.title: <player>
a4d10e12-ee9d-4967-9baa-54f37a016607.text: Yes please, I want to stop receiving vesseled containers.

ae32e1b3-599d-4373-bcc7-2283ca8705d6.title: Arthur the Clue Hunter
ae32e1b3-599d-4373-bcc7-2283ca8705d6.text:
Very well, you'll no longer find clues from mining,
fishing and woodcutting.

c35a2f52-cd63-4c4d-bbac-aa746f98770b.title: Arthur the Clue Hunter
c35a2f52-cd63-4c4d-bbac-aa746f98770b.text:
This type of clue has you talk to someone around
Gielinor. Although the clue does not tell you exactly who
to talk to

45ccd25a-6026-4ba1-a579-0b89ebf1d52d.title: Arthur the Clue Hunter
45ccd25a-6026-4ba1-a579-0b89ebf1d52d.text:
You will see a couple of words that may or may not
make sense together. You will have to rearrange the
letters to make the name of the person you need to talk
to.

ed2aef1b-cbaf-4f9b-adf6-be72ebd20a77.title: Arthur the Clue Hunter
ed2aef1b-cbaf-4f9b-adf6-be72ebd20a77.text:
This type of clue has you work out a logical problem
for the person you need to talk to. This type of
challenge only appears in tiers medium, hard and
elite.

2dbc69b5-9a3d-4bc1-a5fb-2cf246aaada1.title: Arthur the Clue Hunter
2dbc69b5-9a3d-4bc1-a5fb-2cf246aaada1.text:
There are also challenges that will involve you gathering
an item or crafting an item for a certain person.

700f8835-1e22-47d8-a63b-8a7f35464f05.title: Arthur the Clue Hunter
700f8835-1e22-47d8-a63b-8a7f35464f05.text:
This type of clue have you talk to someone around
Gielinor. Although the clue does not tell you exactly who
to talk to. This type of challenge only appears in clue
tiers medium, hard and elite.

4a3940b4-701a-45b4-834a-cd174f35af66.title: Arthur the Clue Hunter
4a3940b4-701a-45b4-834a-cd174f35af66.text:
A ciper is a string of letters that have been scrambled
using the shift cipher method.

548db22f-2c87-4c50-a40e-bc6ad01d2b46.title: Arthur the Clue Hunter
548db22f-2c87-4c50-a40e-bc6ad01d2b46.text:
An example of this would be ZCZL which, shifted
forward by one, would be Adam.

01524095-6771-442a-8b55-574991fa0aba.title: Arthur the Clue Hunter
01524095-6771-442a-8b55-574991fa0aba.text:
This  type of clue will have you use a sextant, chart and
a watch to find out the place you will need to dig. This
type of challenge only appears in clue tiers medium and
above.

1c766dde-9145-443d-9043-eb4a72638ead.title: Arthur the Clue Hunter
1c766dde-9145-443d-9043-eb4a72638ead.text:
After you find the place you need to dig, you may find
a casket or another scroll.

e713e80e-6ef1-4bcc-bc62-e666530252ca.title: Arthur the Clue Hunter
e713e80e-6ef1-4bcc-bc62-e666530252ca.text:
This type of clue can be as simple as talk to the
This type of clue can be as simple as talk to the
specified person or searching a crate in a specified
location.

3e93167e-7d67-4e3f-a2d8-4a447fe1966c.title: Arthur the Clue Hunter
3e93167e-7d67-4e3f-a2d8-4a447fe1966c.text:
But the higher the tier of clue, the more steps you will
have to do beforehwand. An example of this would be
needing to find a key before opening a chest.

6a492ce1-3ad4-4637-ad43-4d62c2cdfc0c.title: Arthur the Clue Hunter
6a492ce1-3ad4-4637-ad43-4d62c2cdfc0c.text:
This type of clue will give you a location that you will
need to visit, along with some items you will need.

73890dd7-db09-4f08-9dd0-57546e18412e.title: Arthur the Clue Hunter
73890dd7-db09-4f08-9dd0-57546e18412e.text:
At this location you will need to perform an emote, as
well as wear the items that you had to bring along.

1b2b132d-ec4c-4c09-847f-29eb3f1712a9.title: Arthur the Clue Hunter
1b2b132d-ec4c-4c09-847f-29eb3f1712a9.text: Some clues may have you wear nothing at all.

09a078d5-4e9b-4a0f-a861-edc30988a3f3.title: Arthur the Clue Hunter
09a078d5-4e9b-4a0f-a861-edc30988a3f3.text: But please don't do that in public!

bd96c8e6-5ae2-441d-a693-b423cd807efb.title: Arthur the Clue Hunter
bd96c8e6-5ae2-441d-a693-b423cd807efb.text:
This type of challenge only appears in clue tiers
medium and above.

2fa9217d-0082-4c9f-92dc-99b69376b50c.title: Arthur the Clue Hunter
2fa9217d-0082-4c9f-92dc-99b69376b50c.text:
Depending on the tier of clue, you will need to obtain a
strange device from either Reldo, located in Varrock, or
Jorral, located south of Tree Gnome Stronghold.

c84d1f7c-7349-413d-bd13-48f737783e3e.title: Arthur the Clue Hunter
c84d1f7c-7349-413d-bd13-48f737783e3e.text:
You will then need to use this device to find the location
you will need to dig.

248c78aa-9946-41b9-8ba0-a1c35fabce3b.title: Arthur the Clue Hunter
248c78aa-9946-41b9-8ba0-a1c35fabce3b.text: You will only need to talk to Reldo for beginner clues.

71e4a1ac-a4ee-4fbb-b0f8-f5a90e3cbaba.title: Arthur the Clue Hunter
71e4a1ac-a4ee-4fbb-b0f8-f5a90e3cbaba.text:
There are many different puzzles that you can come
across while doing clues. These range from light boxes to
puzzle boxes.

8acc6f3c-d1d7-40f5-9729-f6a471d43e89.title: Arthur the Clue Hunter
8acc6f3c-d1d7-40f5-9729-f6a471d43e89.text:
Puzzle boxes are puzzles that will have you complete a 
slider puzzle that, when complete, will look like an image
in game.

230007f8-df14-433a-bd40-615ce6572c24.title: Arthur the Clue Hunter
230007f8-df14-433a-bd40-615ce6572c24.text:
Light boxes are a puzzle which contains a 5 by 5 grid
of lights with some lights on and some lights off.

52258dcc-5d14-4448-bcfd-eebf27f4eea4.title: Arthur the Clue Hunter
52258dcc-5d14-4448-bcfd-eebf27f4eea4.text:
The puzzle will have you click the buttons below to turn
on or off some of the lights with the end goal being,
having all the lights turned on.

c94be012-8f4f-4d91-a804-4ee1e248791b.title: Arthur the Clue Hunter
c94be012-8f4f-4d91-a804-4ee1e248791b.text: This type of clue will show you a map of an area.

d961a970-c849-408e-9a07-f0e1877d4875.title: Arthur the Clue Hunter
d961a970-c849-408e-9a07-f0e1877d4875.text:
This map will show you where you will need to dig, or
what you will need to search to get the next clue.

7f9252e6-c46b-481e-b7d8-a8e421c35d5f.title: Arthur the Clue Hunter
7f9252e6-c46b-481e-b7d8-a8e421c35d5f.text:
This type of clue will show you which fairy ring code
you will need to use to get to the right place to dig.

f9173acb-ff97-427f-bc13-0c5fe44786c3.title: Arthur the Clue Hunter
f9173acb-ff97-427f-bc13-0c5fe44786c3.text:
You will then need to use the numbers to figure out
where you will need to dig after arriving to your
destination.
